    Class and Description
    DiscoveredServer
    Represents a server that has been discovered by the Discovery system.
    DiscoveryHandler
    Used by the Discovery system with the sole purpose of sending received packets to the discovery system so they can be handled.
    DiscoveryListener
    Used to listen for events that occur in the Discovery system.
    DiscoveryMode
    Determines how discovery will be handled by the Discovery system.
    DiscoveryThread
    Used by the Discovery system to server pings in the background.
